      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SATONO GLOW (2) undefeated in two starts. Big jump in class when sent south for a dominant 3 len victory over 1200m in the G3 Thoroughbred Breeders Stakes at Flemington. Has scope for further improvement and not sure where her ceiling is. Maps well and gets her chance. SCREEN ICON (4) talented filly finally drawn a decent barrier. Raced without luck in the three career starts, including the latest eye-catching second over 1200m at this track in the G2 Sweet Embrace. Kept up to the mark with a 1050m tick over trial placing and can race much closer here. Hard to hold out. REACHIN' OUT (9) never headed on debut with an explosive 4 len win over 1100m at Randwick Kensington. Massive rise in class and looks up to the task from the good gate. LUMBINI (3) returns from a let-up after she stalked the speed with a gritty second over 1200m in the G3 Magic Night Stakes at Rosehill. Kept ticking over with a trial 754m trial win at Randwick. Place best from the draw. CIARON'S STAR (5) next best.",
